	   <tr><td colspan=2>I got this today (ironically with my retired Druid who was only coming on to scout PoG for the guild) from a Firiona Vie quest.  She was out and about with a Ranger.<br><br>Basically, they travelled from DL, through BW and off to SF.  I chatted some, assisted a bit and gave some booze to the Ranger who seemed a little stressed.  Firiona talked with a Dragon at the Druid zone-in for a bit, eventually spawning an Ogre who turned into a mini-Cazic (more Avatar sized).  We killed him in due course and went on our way.  There had been talk about VS being the target of our assault but we persuded Firiona that this might not be such a great idea.<br><br>So, I head off to PoG to assist the guild and get summoned out to FV the town.  The lady tosses me a coin for my troubles and I hand it to the girl in the corner as instructed.  Voila, about a blue of exp in 52 and this rather nice belt.  All in all though, I rather wish my main had been there =)<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
